<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idb89f0906-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea" identifier="/us/usc/t5/s6340"><num value="6340">§ 6340.</num><heading> Inapplicability of certain provisions</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Except to the extent that the Office of Personnel Management may prescribe regulations, nothing in section 7351 shall apply with respect to a solicitation, donation, or acceptance of leave under this subchapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idb89f0907-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/100/566/s2/a">Pub. L. 100–566, § 2(a)</ref>, <date date="1988-10-31">Oct. 31, 1988</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/102/2838">102 Stat. 2838</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
